            <sampling>
                <studyExtent>
                    <description>
                        <para>The data were obtained during field research. Expeditionary and stationary methods of observations were used. The methods were used to make a standard geobotanical description.</para>
                    </description>
                </studyExtent>
                <samplingDescription>
                    <para>Species were determined according to Dobrochayeva D. N., et al. The determinant of higher plants of Ukraine, ed. Yu N. N. Prokudin. - K .: Science. opinion, 1987. - 548 p. The names of the species are specified according to Mosyakin S.L., Fedoronchuk M.M. Vascular plants of Ukraine. A nomenclatural checklist. - Kiev, 1999. - 345 pp. Habitats were determined by the method of Brown Blanke.
The coordinates were set using a GPS navigator.</para>
                </samplingDescription>
            </sampling>
